column2: Windy until 1 hour before.  Surf temp 73 F.
Algae bloom.  Sewer smell/septic due to lots of rain.
In the last week- we've had over 8" of rain and unseasonably cool temp.  Surf temp 67 F.
Algae bloom heavy - 40 F air temp.  Surface temp 60 F.
Algae in spot E on October 2.  Water less green on October 7.
Mostly clear of algae but seems more brown and an unusual amount of leaves floating (primarily oak + birch).  Surface temp 46 F.
30 F ambient air temp.  pH approx. 4.5.  Surface temp 43 F.
Weeks of stormy weather.  Partly sunny.  Surf temp 64 F.
A very cool wet spring and summer so far.  Surf temp 65 f

Surf temp 70 F.  Some algae coming slight green color.
Surf temp 67 F.  Green (algae ) clumps (1/4" diameter) floating on surface.
Surf temp 57 F.  Ambient temp this morning was 38 F.
Surf temp 60 F.  Beautiful warm day prior to reading.
Two days of good weather- prior week lots of rain
Surface water temp 65- 3 days w/o rain

Dry week- sunny- surface water temp 71
Surface water temp 75- Assumed time was 12:00.
Some algae- two days warm weather.  Rain previous two days.
Nice summer weather- temps 78-85- little rain- surface water temp 73

Some green algae spots floating on top.
Wind - no rain for last 3 days.
No rain for a week- cool- 25 degrees at night- 50 degrees in the day.
Dark.  Assumed sample time was noon.
Surface temp. 50 degrees F- nice day 70 degrees F.

Surface temp. 63 degrees.  Bright - sunny calm day.
Surface temp. 63 degrees.  After rain and high winds.
Surface temp. 71 degrees.  Warm-hot muggy weather for 1 week.
Surface temp. 82 degrees.  Over a week of plus 90 degrees weather and no rain.

Lots of green algae on surface- surface temp. 58 degrees
58 degrees surface temp. had rain for last 3 days.
Nice warm 85 degrees F for three days.
Surface temp. 70 degrees F. small rains last night.
Surface temp. 74 degrees F. very windy.
Surface temp. 74 degrees. rain brought junk in from mud lake into site e.
Temp. 53 degrees F (water) . beautiful fall day. been rain free for a week.
Sunny- clear to light green water.
sunny day- heavy rain last night
warm day- hazy- and breezy Nice day
